column16: Matt Reynolds grounds into a force out, fielded by third baseman Jeimer Candelario.   Wilmer Flores out at 3rd.
James Loney singles on a line drive to left fielder Matt Szczur.   Juan Lagares scores.    Kelly Johnson to 3rd.    Wilmer Flores to 2nd.
Wilmer Flores singles on a line drive to left fielder Matt Szczur.   Juan Lagares to 3rd.    Kelly Johnson to 2nd.
Kelly Johnson singles on a soft ground ball to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.   Juan Lagares to 2nd.
Brandon Nimmo flies out to right fielder Jason Heyward.
Jacob deGrom flies out to left fielder Matt Szczur.
Juan Lagares singles on a ground ball to center fielder Albert Almora Jr.
Alejandro De Aza grounds out, second baseman Javier Baez to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.
Rene Rivera hit by pitch.    James Loney to 2nd.
